title: Ep. #86 | Catching Up: Jay Park and DJ Wegun
description:
AOMG's very own Jay Park and DJ Wegun drop by to discuss the DJ scene in Korea, all-time favorite Kpop groups, and thoughts about retirement.


Make sure to subscribe to @daebakshow (IT’S FREE) and leave a comment, rating and/or review on Spotify, Apple Podcasts, Soundcloud, and YouTube.
